{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina features views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout of the apartment is ideal for those who want to enjoy beautiful vistas without the need for air conditioning. The living room has a fully equipped kitchen, including appliances such as an induction hob, BOSCH dishwasher, and a microwave. The bedroom has a double bed, nightstands, and wardrobes, while the children's room serves as an office with furniture that suggests it is suitable for children. The bathroom features a bidet shower by the toilet and underfloor electric heating to make the apartment comfortable in both summer and winter. The kitchen is equipped with a sliding table and dining table during dinner, making it perfect for entertaining guests. The building offers security services 24 hours a day and includes a restaurant, dental clinic, client center of the Ministry of Interior of the Slovak Republic, and the headquarters of the real estate agency MGM."}
